<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Given a neutral battlefield where both sets of physics can operate, I have to say that the Federation has an advantage in warp speed combat. They may not win, but they could probably get away. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
